                    <comment id="12524654" author="dpfister" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2007 10:52:38 +0100"  >This bug was initially reported by Markus Reis. A lot of thanks go to him for helping me to setup a JBoss environment where I was able to reproduce this issue. JBoss in fact invoked the following methods on Jackrabbit&amp;#39;s XAResource implementation:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
start(xid, TMNOFLAGS)&lt;br/&gt;
end(xid, TMSUSPEND)&lt;br/&gt;
end(xid, TMSUCCESS)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
which is perfectly legal according to the spec.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Fixed in revision 572595. </comment>
